'''Daniella Cicarelli Lemos''' (born November 6, 1978) is an [[Italy|Italian]]-[[Brazil]]ian former fashion model and TV show hostess for [[MTV Brasil]]'s ''[[Beija Sapo]]''. She was engaged to Brazilian footballer [[Ronaldo (Brazilian footballer)|Ronaldo]] for three months in 2005.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/english/doc/2005-05/12/content_441435.htm |title=China Daily |publisher=China Daily |date=2005-05-12 |accessdate=2012-08-01}}</ref>

==YouTube controversy==
In September 2006, a video of Cicarelli having sex with her boyfriend on a beach in [[Tarifa]], Spain<ref>[http://oglobo.globo.com/cultura/mat/2006/09/28/285875345.asp Justiça mantém liminar que obriga sites a tirar vídeo de Cicarelli com namorado do ar] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080308025739/http://oglobo.globo.com/cultura/mat/2006/09/28/285875345.asp |date=March 8, 2008 }}</ref> was shot by [[paparazzi|paparazzo]] Miguel Temprano and broadcast on the TV show ''Dolce Vita'' on the Spanish station [[Telecinco]]. The video was spread around the internet, with Cicarelli being granted legal injunctions against [[YouTube]] and other websites,<ref>{{cite web |url=http://idgnow.uol.com.br/internet/2006/09/21/idgnoticia.2006-09-21.3066359412 |title=Cicarelli processa Globo, iG e YouTube por causa de vídeo de paparazzo - Internet - IDG Now! |publisher=Idgnow.uol.com.br |date=2006-09-21 |accessdate=2012-08-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120618180255/http://idgnow.uol.com.br/internet/2006/09/21/idgnoticia.2006-09-21.3066359412/ |archivedate=2012-06-18 |df= }}</ref> leading to several Brazilian ISPs blocking YouTube. In January 2007 after a legal decision, YouTube was blocked in Brazil for two days, resulting in 5.7 million users being blocked.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/6233693.stm | work=BBC News | title=Brazil model wins YouTube battle | date=January 5, 2007}}</ref> This decision was criticized by internet watch groups for being an extremely selfish act. This happened when Cicarelli worked as a host on MTV Brasil, provoking a torrent of nearly 80,000 emails protesting against the blockade and her legal actions. Some people even went to the building of the TV station to protest.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gulp.com.br/noticia/protesto-na-mtv-contra-cicarelli |title=Protesto na MTV contra Cicarelli Gulp Â¬ Links Â¬Â¬ by Gulp Â¬ Links Â¬Â¬ |publisher=Gulp.com.br |date=2007-01-13 |accessdate=2012-08-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Louis Belanger, Canada |url=http://globalvoices.org/2007/01/12/cicarelli-case-censorship-and-boycott-dialectics-in-the-brazilian-blogosphere |title=Cicarelli Case: Censorship and Boycott Dialectics in the Brazilian Blogosphere · Global Voices |publisher=Globalvoices.org |date=2007-01-12 |accessdate=2012-08-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.terra.com.br/istoegente/386/reportagens/capa_cicarelli.htm |title=ISTOÉ Gente |publisher=Terra.com.br |date= |accessdate=2012-08-01}}</ref>

In 2007, YouTube won the case, based on the fact that there is no expectation of privacy on a public beach. Cicarelli appealed and in 2008 the Supreme Court of the state of São Paulo changed the decision, on grounds of lack of public interest and invasion of privacy.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://idgnow.uol.com.br/internet/2008/06/12/daniella-cicarelli-ganha-acao-contra-youtube-em-bloqueio-de-video |title=Daniella Cicarelli ganha ação contra YouTube em bloqueio de vídeo - Internet - IDG Now! |publisher=Idgnow.uol.com.br |date= |accessdate=2012-08-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080615181704/http://idgnow.uol.com.br/internet/2008/06/12/daniella-cicarelli-ganha-acao-contra-youtube-em-bloqueio-de-video/ |archivedate=2008-06-15 |df= }}</ref> The lawsuit isn't finished yet, because YouTube appealed and now wait for the judgment by the Federal Supreme Court. YouTube remains active in Brazil.<ref>[https://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601109&sid=a_17Uu0NazR0&refer=exclusive Sex Video of Merrill Banker, MTV Host Eclipses Brazil Election], Bloomberg.com, September 29, 2006.</ref><ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/americas/6233693.stm Brazil model wins YouTube battle ], BBC News, January 5, 2007</ref><ref>{{Pt_icon}} [http://conjur.estadao.com.br/static/text/51792,1 A Dona da Ação - Cicarelli é autora do processo contra o YouTube]</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Anderson |first=Nate |url=https://arstechnica.com/news.ars/post/20070627-youtube-wins-privacy-case-against-brazilian-supermodel.html |title=YouTube wins "supermodel sex on the beach" case |publisher=Arstechnica.com |date=2007-06-28 |accessdate=2012-08-01}}</ref>

