'''Padang''' is an ethnic group in [[Sudan]], a subgroup of the [[Dinka people|Dinka]].<ref name=Dinka>{{cite web|title=People Profile: The Dinka of South Sudan|url=http://strategyleader.org/profiles/dinka.html|publisher=Strategy Leader|accessdate=7 January 2013}}</ref> They speak [[Padang language|Padang]], a [[Dinka language]]. Many members of this ethnicity are Christians. The population of this ethnicity exceeds 100,000.

